## Superseded from config-filename-validation

```yaml
name: config-filename-validation
description: "Skill: Config Filename/ID Validation Pattern"
category: tooling
date: 2026-03-19
version: "2.0.0"
```

`validate_filename_tier_consistency()` / `validate_filename_model_id_consistency()` pattern:
skip `_`-prefixed fixtures, emit warnings (not errors), call after dataclass construction.
For configs with no ID field use stem-only check; document why field-level check is skipped.
Covers Issues #733 (tier), #806 (defaults stem-only); PRs #795, #941.

