## Superseded from python-version-alignment

```yaml
name: python-version-alignment
description: "Align Python version across pyproject.toml, pixi.toml, Dockerfile, and CI test matrix."
category: tooling
date: 2026-03-25
version: "3.0.0"
verification: verified-local
```

Three-part workflow: (A) Dockerfile alignment ‚Äî update `FROM` and site-packages path;
(B) CI matrix expansion ‚Äî replace pixi with `setup-python + pip install -e ".[dev]"`,
restrict coverage upload to one version; (C) Add new Python stable release to matrix.
Critical: pixi ignores `actions/setup-python`; matrix expansion alone has no effect.
Verified: ProjectHephaestus #44/#75, #58/#112; ProjectScylla #1118/#1166.

