## Superseded from config-env-double-underscore-nesting

```yaml
name: config-env-double-underscore-nesting
description: "Fix ambiguous env var to config key mapping by using __ as nesting delimiter."
category: architecture
date: 2026-03-25
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-local
```

Replace `.replace("_", ".")` with `.split("__")`. `__` = nesting delimiter; single `_`
preserved as literal character in key segment. Convention matches Django/Flask patterns.
Issue HomericIntelligence/ProjectHephaestus#29, PR #67; 389 unit tests pass.

