## Superseded from config-loader-schema-validation

```yaml
name: config-loader-schema-validation
description: "TRIGGER CONDITIONS: Fixing a config loader method that bypasses schema validation by calling _load_yaml() directly."
category: architecture
date: 2026-03-07
version: 1.0.0
```

`load()` aggregation method called `_load_yaml()` on `defaults.yaml` directly, bypassing
`load_defaults()` (which applies Pydantic validation, filename checks, JSON schema checks).
Fix: route through `load_defaults()`; replace manual dict mapping with typed attribute access.
Test `TestLoadMergedConfigSchemaValidation` verifies validation now participates in merge path.
Issue #1436, PR #1462; ProjectScylla 4566 unit tests, 75.84% coverage.

---

## Superseded from config-dir-consolidation

```yaml
name: config-dir-consolidation
description: "Move config files from a dedicated config/ directory into tests/ when config is only consumed by test infrastructure."
category: architecture
date: 2026-02-19
version: 1.0.0
```

Ten-step workflow: audit, create stripped YAML at new location, refactor loader class,
update auto-detection paths, remove prompt injection from adapters/runners, update model
classes, update tests, delete old directory with `git rm -r`, update docs/scripts, verify.
18 files deleted, 15 modified, 2202 tests passing. Pre-existing bug discovered during
E2E dry run (`TierConfig` missing `language` field ‚Äî unrelated to consolidation).

