## Superseded from json-schema-validation-wiring

```yaml
name: json-schema-validation-wiring
description: Wire JSON schema validation into config loader methods (load_test, load_rubric).
category: testing
date: 2026-03-19
version: 1.0.0
```

Audit fixtures vs schema before updating (check field names, ID patterns). Wire
`_validate_schema()` after `_load_yaml()` before Pydantic construction; use `_`-prefix
guard consistently. Updated `test.schema.json` (added `language` required, `tiers` optional,
broadened `id` pattern) and `rubric.schema.json` (added `categories` alternative, optional
fields). 18 new tests. PR #1465, Issue #1438.

