## Superseded from config-filename-model-id-audit

```yaml
name: config-filename-model-id-audit
description: Audit and fix YAML config files where filename stems mismatch model_id fields
category: testing
date: 2026-02-19
version: 1.0.0
```

Run `ConfigLoader('.').load_all_models()` (pass project root, not `'config'`) to discover
mismatches. Rename with `git mv` (preserves history). Grep for stale short-form IDs in
source. Write `TestLoadAllModels` regression class with `caplog` for warning assertions.
3 files renamed, 9 tests added, 2214 total passing. Issue #732, follow-up from #692.

