## Superseded from wire-schema-validation

```yaml
name: wire-schema-validation
description: "TRIGGER CONDITIONS: Wiring JSON schema validation into a config loader that already parses YAML into dataclass/Pydantic models."
category: testing
date: 2026-03-04
version: 1.0.0
```

`_SCHEMAS_DIR` and `_validate_schema()` must be placed **after all imports** in `loader.py`
(ruff-format reorders import blocks; helpers placed between stdlib and local imports leave
`ConfigurationError` undefined at definition time). Wire after `_load_yaml()`, before Pydantic
construction; guard with `if not name.startswith("_"):`. Fix Pydantic alias mismatches in
fixtures (YAML key must be the `alias=` value). 15 new tests in `TestSchemaValidation`.
PR #1424, Issue #1380.
